The paper discusses the training of recurrent neural networks for learning symbolic data sequences, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the modeling of complex algorithmic constraints, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL) and sequence analysis (cs.SD).
